o attract more customers to my bike store'). If you wish to talk to Kodee, close this window and continue in the chat.","chatbot.widget.about.yourself":"Tell us about yourself","chatbot.widget.add.file":"Add file","chatbot.widget.agent.name.ally":"Customer Comms","chatbot.widget.agent.name.arrow":"Sales & Outreach","chatbot.widget.agent.name.buzz":"Marketing Planner","chatbot.widget.agent.name.north":"Business Advisor","chatbot.widget.agent.name.quill":"Creative Writer","chatbot.widget.agent.name.scout":"SEO Consultant","chatbot.widget.agent.name.shield":"Legal Advisor","chatbot.widget.agentInProgress.status":"{agentName} is working on it…","chatbot.widget.agentRedirect.ally.description":"Customer Comms can craft empathetic customer service responses, develop comprehensive FAQ documentation, design email onboarding sequences, and standardize your support tone — going much deeper than I can in a chat.","chatbot.widget.agentRedirect.arrow.description":"Sales & Outreach can build targeted prospect lists, write personalized cold email sequences, formulate objection-handling scripts, and design your sales funnel — going much deeper than I can in a chat.","chatbot.widget.agentRedirect.badge":"AI Agent","chatbot.widget.agentRedirect.buzz.description":"Marketing Planner can design multi-channel marketing campaigns, allocate your advertising budget, map out promotional calendars, and define your target audience segments — going much deeper than I can in a chat.","chatbot.widget.agentRedirect.north.description":"Business Advisor can analyze your business model, evaluate market opportunities, construct detailed financial forecasts, and develop a strategic growth roadmap — going much deeper than I can in a chat.","chatbot.widget.agentRedirect.quill.description":"Creative Writer can draft compelling blog posts, develop engaging brand narratives, write long-form articles, and refine your overall content strategy — going much deeper than I can in a chat.","chatbot.widget.agentRedirect.scout.description":"SEO Consultant can run a comprehensive SEO audit of your website, analyze your keyword rankings, identify technical issues, and create an actionable optimization plan — going much deeper than I can in a chat.","chatbot.widget.agentRedirect.shield.description":"Legal Advisor can review your business contracts, highlight potential compliance risks, outline standard legal frameworks, and help draft basic terms of service — going much deeper than I can in a chat.","chatbot.widget.agentRedirect.tryButton":"Try {agentName}","chatbot.widget.agentResponse.viewWork":"View {agentName}'s work","chatbot.widget.agentsTopUp.cta":"Top up credits","chatbot.widget.agentsTopUp.description":"Top up your Agent credits or upgrade your plan to keep going.","chatbot.widget.agentsTopUp.title":"You've run out of Agent credits","chatbot.widget.banner.message.generic":"Some Hostinger services may be experiencing issues. Our team is working to restore normal functionality.","chatbot.widget.banner.modal.seeAll":"See all","chatbot.widget.banner.modal.title":"Service updates","chatbot.widget.code.block.copied":"Copied","chatbot.widget.code.block.copy":"Copy","chatbot.widget.colleague.will.join.soon":"A colleague will join soon. If you want to continue chatting with Kodee, you can leave the queue.","chatbot.widget.confirmationButton.confirm":"Confirm","chatbot.widget.confirmationButton.deny":"Deny","chatbot.widget.cost.limit.modal.description":"We’re working on upgrade options to increase your weekly Kodee limit. You’ll be able to get higher limits and improved performance soon.","chatbot.widget.cost.limit.modal.title":"Higher limits are coming","chatbot.widget.costLimit.banner.cta":"Upgrade","chatbot.widget.costLimit.banner.description":"Keep chatting with Kodee's lighter version until your limit resets on {resetDate}.","chatbot.widget.costLimit.banner.title":"You’ve reached your weekly Kodee limit.","chatbot.widget.costLimit.modal.cancel":"Cancel","chatbot.widget.costLim