ct","chatbot.widget.suggestions.changeCurrentDomainOfTheBuilderWebsite.description":"Update your Builder website to use a new domain","chatbot.widget.suggestions.changeCurrentDomainOfTheBuilderWebsite.prompt":"I want to switch my Builder site from one domain to new domain. Can you update it?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.changeCurrentDomainOfTheBuilderWebsite.title":"Change website domain","chatbot.widget.suggestions.changeProductPrice.prompt":"Can you help me change the price for a product in my store? I'd like to update the pricing.","chatbot.widget.suggestions.changeProductPrice.title":"Change product price","chatbot.widget.suggestions.checkDomainAvailability.description":"See if a domain is available and explore alternatives","chatbot.widget.suggestions.checkDomainAvailability.prompt":"Help me check if a domain name is available for registration. Ask me for all the information you need upfront","chatbot.widget.suggestions.checkDomainAvailability.title":"Check domain availability","chatbot.widget.suggestions.checkSshConnectivity.description":"Verify whether the SSH service is reachable on your VPS","chatbot.widget.suggestions.checkSshConnectivity.prompt":"Check if the SSH service is reachable for my VPS. determine if SSH access is properly configured and the service is running,","chatbot.widget.suggestions.checkSshConnectivity.title":"Check SSH Connectivity","chatbot.widget.suggestions.clearWebsiteCache.prompt":"Clear my website cache or troubleshoot cache-related issues that may be affecting my site.","chatbot.widget.suggestions.clearWebsiteCache.title":"Clear website cache","chatbot.widget.suggestions.clientIntroductionKeyPoints.prompt":"What are key points to include when introducing myself to a new client?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.clientIntroductionKeyPoints.title":"What are key points to include when introducing myself to a new client?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.connectEmailWithThirdPartyApps.prompt":"How can I connect my email account on third-party ap