er.prompt":"Help me renew my current subscription. Confirm renewal availability, provide a cost estimate, and create a renewal order.","chatbot.widget.suggestions.createRenewalOrder.title":"Renew Your Subscription","chatbot.widget.suggestions.createSubdomain.prompt":"Create a subdomain for my website. Please add a new subdomain under my main domain. For example, create blog.mysite.com.","chatbot.widget.suggestions.createSubdomain.title":"Create a subdomain","chatbot.widget.suggestions.createSubdomainForVhost.description":"Create a subdomain easily","chatbot.widget.suggestions.createSubdomainForVhost.prompt":"I'd like to create a subdomain for my website. Please add a new subdomain under my main domain. For example, create my site","chatbot.widget.suggestions.createSubdomainForVhost.title":"Create a subdomain","chatbot.widget.suggestions.createVpsSnapshot.description":"Capture the current state of your VPS","chatbot.widget.suggestions.createVpsSnapshot.prompt":"I'd like to capture the current state of my VPS. Please create a snapshot so I have a backup of how it is right now. Can you take a new snapshot of my virtual machine?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.createVpsSnapshot.title":"Create a VPS snapshot","chatbot.widget.suggestions.createWebsiteForDomain.prompt":"Help me create a new website for my domain. Help me pick the CMS (Builder, WP, Horizons, other) and guide me through the steps to create it or create it for me if possible.","chatbot.widget.suggestions.createWebsiteForDomain.title":"Create website","chatbot.widget.suggestions.createWordpressStagingEnvironment.description":"Make a copy of your WordPress site for testing changes safely","chatbot.widget.suggestions.createWordpressStagingEnvironment.prompt":"I want to test changes before going live. Can you create a staging site for my WordPress installation?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.createWordpressStagingEnvironment.title":"Create WordPress staging site","chatbot.widget.suggestions.deleteMigrationRequest.desc