w VPS Action Logs","chatbot.widget.suggestions.getVirtualMachineBackups.description":"Check what backups are available for your VPS See the available VPS backups","chatbot.widget.suggestions.getVirtualMachineBackups.prompt":"I want to check what backups are available for my VPS. Please show me the list of existing backups. Can you retrieve the backups for my virtual machine?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.getVirtualMachineBackups.title":"Check VPS backups","chatbot.widget.suggestions.getVirtualMachineDetails.description":"See the details of your VPS","chatbot.widget.suggestions.getVirtualMachineDetails.prompt":"I'd like to see the details of my VPS. Can you show me its configuration and specifications? Please display the full information for my virtual machine.","chatbot.widget.suggestions.getVirtualMachineDetails.title":"Check VPS details","chatbot.widget.suggestions.getVirtualMachineMetrics.description":"See your VPS CPU/memory usage and more","chatbot.widget.suggestions.getVirtualMachineMetrics.prompt":"I want to check the performance of my VPS. Please show me the CPU, memory, and other usage stats. Can you give me the current metrics for my virtual machine?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.getVirtualMachineMetrics.title":"Check VPS performance","chatbot.widget.suggestions.hideProduct.prompt":"Can you hide a product from my store? I want to keep it but not show it to customers right now.","chatbot.widget.suggestions.hideProduct.title":"Hide product","chatbot.widget.suggestions.improveSeo.prompt":`Create a benchmark analysis showing how top-performing websites differ from average ones across SEO, content depth, brand clarity, UX, page structure, CTAs, and site speed.

