ate a renewal order for me.","chatbot.widget.suggestions.renewDomain.title":"Domain renewal","chatbot.widget.suggestions.renewalPriceCheck.prompt":"How do I check my current hosting plan and renew price? Make a short list of my invoices that are near expiration date and the related services.","chatbot.widget.suggestions.renewalPriceCheck.title":"Price for renewing my subscription","chatbot.widget.suggestions.resendTransferEmail.description":"Send the transfer authorization email again for your domain","chatbot.widget.suggestions.resendTransferEmail.prompt":"Resend the transfer authorization email again for my domain transfer","chatbot.widget.suggestions.resendTransferEmail.title":"Resend Domain Transfer Email","chatbot.widget.suggestions.resetOrRemoveWordpress.prompt":"Delete, uninstall, or reset my WordPress website and explain what data will be removed before proceeding.","chatbot.widget.suggestions.resetOrRemoveWordpress.title":"Reset or remove WordPress","chatbot.widget.suggestions.retrieveAllDnsRecordsForADomain.description":"See existing domain DNS records","chatbot.widget.suggestions.retrieveAllDnsRecordsForADomain.prompt":"I need to see the DNS records for my domain. Can you show me all the current records associated with it? Please fetch the DNS details.","chatbot.widget.suggestions.retrieveAllDnsRecordsForADomain.title":"Check DNS records","chatbot.widget.suggestions.retrieveAllUserStores.description":"See a list of all your active stores created with Hostinger Builder","chatbot.widget.suggestions.retrieveAllUserStores.prompt":"List all my stores made with Hostinger website builder.","chatbot.widget.suggestions.retrieveAllUserStores.title":"View Your Stores","chatbot.widget.suggestions.reviewStorePerformance.prompt":"I'd like to review my store's performance. Can you show me analytics and insights about sales and products?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.reviewStorePerformance.title":"Review store performance","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesBusinessEmailForTeam.prompt":"Hi! I need email accounts for a small team. How do I choose the right plan and how many mailboxes do I need?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesBusinessEmailForTeam.title":"Email for my team","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesBusinessEmailGmailOutlook.prompt":"Hi! If I buy Business Email, can I use it in Gmail or Outlook apps? How would I log in and set it up?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesBusinessEmailGmailOutlook.title":"Can I use your email in Gmail or Outlook?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesBusinessEmailMigrate.prompt":"Hi! I already have email with another provider. Can you explain how migration works and which plan I should buy?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesBusinessEmailMigrate.title":"Can I move my existing email?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesBusinessEmailProfessional.prompt":"Hi! I want an email like name{'@'}mydomain.com. Which Business Email plan should I choose and how do I set it up?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesBusinessEmailProfessional.title":"I want a professional email address","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesBusinessEmailUseDomain.prompt":"Hi! I already have a domain name. Can I connect it to Business Email, and what steps do I need to take?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesBusinessEmailUseDomain.title":"Can I use my domain for email?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesBusinessEmailWhatsIncluded.prompt":"Hi! What features are included in your Business Email plans (storage, security, spam protection, etc.) and which plan is best value?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesBusinessEmailWhatsIncluded.title":"What's included in Business Email?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesChooseHostingPlan.prompt":"Hi! I need help choosing a hosting plan. Can you suggest the best option for my website and needs?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesChooseHostingPlan.title":"I need help choosing the right hosting plan","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesCreateWebsite.prompt":"Hi! I want to create a website. Can you guide me on the best way to create a site and recommend a hosting plan?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesCreateWebsite.title":"I want to create a website","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesHorizonsChoosePlan.prompt":"Hi! I want to try Horizons but I'm not sure which plan to choose. Can you recommend the best plan for a first-time project?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesHorizonsChoosePlan.title":"Help me choose a Horizons plan","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesHorizonsCost.prompt":"Hi! Can you explain the total cost to get started with Horizons (what's included in the plan, renewals, and anything else I might need) and recommend the best-value option?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesHorizonsCost.title":"What's the real cost to get started?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesHorizonsIsRight.prompt":"Hi! I'm looking at Horizons and I have an idea for a website or web app. Can you tell me if Horizons is a good fit and what plan I should choose?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesHorizonsIsRight.title":"Is Horizons right for my idea?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesHorizonsLoginsPayments.prompt":"Hi! My project needs features like user accounts and/or payments. Can Horizons handle that, and what would the setup look like?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesHorizonsLoginsPayments.title":"Can I build features like logins/payments?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesHorizonsPublish.prompt":"Hi! If I build something with Horizons, how do I publish it online and connect a domain? What do I need to purchase to go live?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesHorizonsPublish.title":"How do I publish what I build?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesHorizonsVsWebsiteBuilder.prompt":"Hi! I'm deciding between Horizons and Website Builder. Can you explain the difference and recommend which one I should buy for my project?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesHorizonsVsWebsiteBuilder.title":"Horizons vs Website Builder","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesMigrateToHostinger.prompt":"Hi! I want to migrate to Hostinger. Can you help me pick the best plan and explain my migration options?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesMigrateToHostinger.title":"I want to migrate to Hostinger","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesN8nChoosePlan.prompt":"Hi! I'm planning to run n8n workflows and I'm not sure which plan fits. Can you recommend a plan based on how I'll use n8n?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesN8nChoosePlan.title":"Help me choose a plan for n8n","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesN8nInstallOnHostinger.prompt":"Hi! I want to install n8n on Hostinger. Can you guide me through the easiest setup step by step?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesN8nInstallOnHostinger.title":"How do I install n8n on Hostinger?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesN8nMonthlyCost.prompt":"Hi! What's the total monthly cost to run self-hosted n8n on Hostinger (hosting + any recommended add-ons), and what's the best-value option?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesN8nMonthlyCost.title":"How much will n8n cost monthly?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesN8nWorkflowVolume.prompt":"Hi! I plan to run multiple workflows and integrations. Ask me questions to help decide what resources (RAM/CPU/storage) I should choose so n8n stays reliable?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesN8nWorkflowVolume.title":"Which n8n plan should I choose to handle my workflow volume?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesOpenclawAiCredits.prompt":"Hi! I saw that I can buy AI credits/tokens for OpenClaw. Can you explain how that works (nexos.ai access, top-ups, usage), and what I should choose to start with?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesOpenclawAiCredits.title":"How do AI credits/tokens work on Hostinger?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesOpenclawIsRightForMe.prompt":"Hi! I'm looking at OpenClaw, but I'm not sure if it fits my use case. I want to use AI across messaging apps (like WhatsApp/Telegram/Slack/Discord). Can you ask a few questions and tell me if OpenClaw is the right choice—and what I should buy to get started on Hostinger?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesOpenclawIsRightForMe.title":"Is OpenClaw right for what I want to build?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesOpenclawSecurity.prompt":"Hi! Privacy matters to me. If I run OpenClaw on a Hostinger VPS, where do my chat logs and data live, how do I keep them under my control, and what security best practices should I enable before going live?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesOpenclawSecurity.title":"Is self-hosted OpenClaw secure and private?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesOpenclawVpsPlan.prompt":"Do I need a VPS to host OpenClaw on Hostinger?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesOpenclawVpsPlan.title":"What plan do I need for OpenClaw?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesVpsChoosePlan.prompt":"Hi! I want to buy a VPS but I don't know which plan to pick. Can you recommend the right VPS plan based on what I'm building and my budget?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesVpsChoosePlan.title":"Help me choose a VPS plan","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesVpsDoINeed.prompt":"Hi! I'm looking at VPS hosting but I'm not sure if it's the right choice for me. Can you ask a few questions about my project and recommend the best option?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesVpsDoINeed.title":"Do I need VPS hosting?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesVpsTooTechnical.prompt":"Hi! I'm interested in VPS. How does management work, and what help or guidance do you provide?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesVpsTooTechnical.title":"Is VPS too technical for me?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesVpsVsWebHosting.prompt":"Hi! Should I choose VPS hosting or regular web hosting for my website/project? Please compare them and tell me what you recommend for my situation.","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesVpsVsWebHosting.title":"VPS vs Web Hosting","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWebHostingChoosePlan.prompt":"Hi! I want to create a website (business/blog/portfolio). Can you recommend the best web hosting plan for me and explain why?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWebHostingChoosePlan.title":"Which hosting plan should I buy?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWebHostingOnlineStore.prompt":"Hi! I want to sell online. Is regular web hosting enough, and which plan should I choose to start?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWebHostingOnlineStore.title":"Is web hosting enough for an online store?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWebHostingTransfer.prompt":"Hi! I already have a website with another provider. Can you tell me how moving to Hostinger works and which hosting plan I should buy?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWebHostingTransfer.title":"I have a site elsewhere — can I transfer it?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWebHostingWhatsIncluded.prompt":"Hi! What exactly is included with your web hosting plans (SSL, email, backups, domain options, etc.) and which plan is the best value?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWebHostingWhatsIncluded.title":"What's included in web hosting?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWebsiteBuilderChoosePlan.prompt":"Hi! I want to use your Website Builder. Can you recommend the right plan for my site and explain the differences between the options?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWebsiteBuilderChoosePlan.title":"Help me pick a Website Builder plan","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWebsiteBuilderOnlineStore.prompt":"Hi! I want to sell products or services online. Can I do that with your Website Builder, and which plan do I need?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWebsiteBuilderOnlineStore.title":"Can I build an online store with Website Builder?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWebsiteBuilderOrWordpress.prompt":"Hi! I want to build a website but I'm not sure if I should use Website Builder or WordPress. Can you help me choose based on what I'm trying to make?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWebsiteBuilderOrWordpress.title":"Should I choose Builder or WordPress?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWebsiteBuilderProfessional.prompt":"Hi! I want a professional-looking website but don't know what layout or sections I need. Can you guide me on what to include and recommend the best plan to start?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWebsiteBuilderProfessional.title":"I want a site that looks professional","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWebsiteBuilderWhatsIncluded.prompt":"Hi! Before I buy, can you explain what's included in the Website Builder plan (features, limits, and anything extra I might need)?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWebsiteBuilderWhatsIncluded.title":"What do I get with the plan?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWordpressChoosePlan.prompt":"Hi! I want to build a WordPress website. Can you recommend the right WordPress hosting plan after figuring out my needs and budget?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWordpressChoosePlan.title":"Which WordPress plan should I buy?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWordpressSetup.prompt":"Hi! I'm new to WordPress. Can you guide me on how to get started and tell me which plan I should buy?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWordpressSetup.title":"Can you help me set up WordPress?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWordpressSpeed.prompt":"Hi! Speed matters to me. Which WordPress hosting plan should I choose to keep my site fast, and what features help with performance?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWordpressSpeed.title":"Will my WordPress site be fast?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWordpressTransfer.prompt":"Hi! I already have a WordPress site with another provider. Can you explain the migration options and recommend the best plan for moving?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWordpressTransfer.title":"Can I transfer my WordPress site to Hostinger?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWordpressVsWebHosting.prompt":"Hi! What's the difference between WordPress hosting and regular web hosting, and which one should I choose?","chatbot.widget.suggestions.salesWordpressVsWebHosting.title":"WordPress hosting vs web hosting","chatbot.widget.suggestions.setupEmail.prompt":"How do I set up or configure my email with my domain?","chatbot.widget